[The size of the at risk population currently under investigation appears to be approximately 5000 individuals. Unfortunately due to cultural reasons, many of the at risk group may not come forward for testing for fear of personal as well as professional security. The time period under investigation is from 26 Apr to 6 May 2020. Hopefully many of the countries rushing to lift lockdown restrictions while they are still confirming hundreds and in some cases thousands of new infections each day will reconsider rushing to lift restrictions prematurely, before it is realistic and feasible to do contact tracing of all newly confirmed cases. - Mod.MPP]

